now wire connection

SH1106 OLED (I2C) — Stopwatch
ST7735 TFT (SPI) — System Stats
Here are the connections:

SH1106 OLED (I2C)
OLED Pin  	NodeMCU Pin
VCC	      3.3V
GND	      GND
SDA      	D2
SCL      	D1

ST7735 TFT (SPI)
TFT Pin  	NodeMCU Pin
VCC    	  3.3V
GND	      GND
CS	      D8
DC	      D3
RST      	D4
SDA       (MOSI)	D7
SCK      	D5
LED	      3.3V


Both displays share 3.3V and GND. Everything else is separate pins. That's all the connections needed.
